Title: Avoid host down via SmartPING out of check period
Level: 1
Edition: cee
Component: cmc
Class: fix
State: unknown
Version: 1.2.5i4
Date: 1403277718
Targetversion: future

If a host was not in its check period and SmartPING was used
as host check then the host would be marked as down nevertheless.
This has been fixed.
